{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843454322,"sessionID":"ses_2877b76d4ffeKKOb4j15pM2jaz","part":{"id":"prt_d7884a8920018toUgb4ih4RyMo","messageID":"msg_d78849c9b001C70rfxxqkmICj2","sessionID":"ses_2877b76d4ffeKKOb4j15pM2jaz","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_b05305055379469a858ed8fd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Core Handlers\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - Add `CreateSandboxRequest`, `CreateSandboxResponse`, `SandboxEntryPoint` types with Validate() method\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` - Constants: DefaultSandboxTTL, DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout, label/annotation keys (SessionID, WorkloadName, SandboxName, IdleTimeout)\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/informers.go` - GVR variables (SandboxGVR, SandboxClaimGVR), Informers struct, Start() and WaitForCacheSync() methods\n15: - [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_controller.go` - SandboxReconciler struct, WatchSandboxOnce() returning channel, getSandboxStatus()\n16: - [ ] **1.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client.go` - K8sClient struct with dynamic client, informer factory, listers; ClientCache for per-user clients; GetOrCreateUserK8sClient()\n17: - [ ] **1.6** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleAgentRuntimeCreate() handler function\n18: - [ ] **1.7** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleCodeInterpreterCreate() handler function\n19: - [ ] **1.8** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` - Register new routes POST /v1/agent-runtime, POST /v1/code-interpreter\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## Phase 2: Workload Builder\n24: \n25: - [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - buildSandboxObject() converting AgentRuntime to Sandbox unstructured object\n26: - [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - buildSandboxClaimObject() for WarmPool path\n27: - [ ] **2.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - buildEntryPoints() to construct SandboxEntryPoint array from podIP and TargetPorts\n28: - [ ] **2.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - resolvePodIP() with annotation, lister, and ownerReference fallback logic\n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ## Phase 3: Sandbox Creator\n33: \n34: - [ ] **3.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - sandboxCreator struct with k8sClient, sandboxController, storeClient, publicKey fields\n35: - [ ] **3.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - createSandbox() method implementing full flow (watcher registration → store placeholder → CR create → wait running → resolve IP → store update)\n36: - [ ] **3.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - rollback logic for CR deletion and store cleanup on timeout/failure\n37: - [ ] **3.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - Handle WarmPoolSize > 0 path (create SandboxClaim vs Sandbox)\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## Phase 4: Auth & GC\n42: \n43: - [ ] **4.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth.go` - authMiddleware with token validation, context keys (userToken, serviceAccount, serviceAccountName, namespace)\n44: - [ ] **4.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth.go` - validateServiceAccountToken() using TokenReview API\n45: - [ ] **4.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - garbageCollector struct with store client and k8sClient\n46: - [ ] **4.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - gcLoop() for periodic cleanup of expired sandboxes\n47: - [ ] **4.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - cleanupExpiredSandboxes() with 2-minute tick interval\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## Phase 5: Error Handling\n52: \n53: - [ ] **5.1** Implement error types: ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound, ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound, ErrTemplateMissing\n54: - [ ] **5.2** Map error types to HTTP status codes in handlers (400 for validation, 401 for auth, 404 for not found, 500 for internal)\n55: - [ ] **5.3** Add error response DTOs in types.go (ErrorResponse with Message field)\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## Phase 6: Integration Points\n60: \n61: - [ ] **6.1** Integrate with client-go: import AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface, SharedInformerFactory\n62: - [ ] **6.2** Integrate with Store: call StoreSandbox(), UpdateSandbox(), DeleteSandboxBySessionID()\n63: - [ ] **6.3** Integrate with SandboxReconciler: call WatchSandboxOnce() for status waiting\n64: \n65: ---\n66: \n67: ## Phase 7: Unit Tests\n68: \n69: - [ ] **7.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestBuildSandboxObject_ValidRuntime\n70: - [ ] **7.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestBuildSandboxClaimObject_WarmPool\n71: - [ ] **7.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestBuildEntryPoints_DefaultPorts\n72: - [ ] **7.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestResolvePodIP_FromAnnotation\n73: - [ ] **7.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestResolvePodIP_FromOwnerReference\n74: - [ ] **7.6** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator_test.go` - TestCreateSandbox_Success\n75: - [ ] **7.7** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator_test.go` - TestCreateSandbox_Timeout\n76: - [ ] **7.8** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator_test.go` - TestCreateSandbox_RollbackOnFailure\n77: - [ ] **7.9** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_Success\n78: - [ ] **7.10** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_MissingPodTemplate\n79: - [ ] **7.11** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_WarmPool\n80: - [ ] **7.12** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_AuthModePicoD\n81: - [ ] **7.13** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go` - TestCreateSandboxRequest_Validate table-driven tests\n82: - [ ] **7.14** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth_test.go` - TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken\n83: - [ ] **7.15** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth_test.go` - TestAuthMiddleware_MissingToken\n84: - [ ] **7.16** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - TestGarbageCollector_ExpiredSandbox\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## Phase 8: Integration Tests\n89: \n90: - [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go` - E2E test with real K8s cluster (TestE2E_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox)\n91: - [ ] **8.2** Test warm pool pre-provisioning with CodeInterpreter WarmPoolSize > 0\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## Phase 9: Verification\n96: \n97: - [ ] **9.1** Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - successful compilation\n98: - [ ] **9.2** Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - all unit tests pass\n99: - [ ] **9.3** Run `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no race conditions\n100: - [ ] **9.4** Run `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no issues\n101: - [ ] **9.5** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - linter passes\n102: - [ ] **9.6** Verify test coverage > 40% with `go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n103: \n104: ---\n105: \n106: ## Dependencies\n107: \n108: | Task | Depends On |\n109: |------|------------|\n110: | Phase 1 | AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架), client-go library |\n111: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 (types, defaults, informers) |\n112: | Phase 3 | Phase 1 + Phase 2 |\n113: | Phase 4 | Phase 1 (k8s_client) |\n114: | Phase 5 | Phase 1 (types) |\n115: | Phase 6 | client-go, store package, SandboxReconciler |\n116: | Phase 7 | Phase 1-5 (implementation